    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity Maze is a 2D physics maze game in which you can customize the maze and get balls to the end by changing gravity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tYou can create custom size mazes that can be  randomly generated or you can create your own maze. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133980/extras/7b836e19de47af677a956e6c6fb47a0b.webp?t=1771619706\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133980/extras/7b836e19de47af677a956e6c6fb47a0b.poster.avif?t=1771619706\" class=\"bb_img\" width=412 height=213 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tChallenge yourself by getting the balls to the end or just have physics fun.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133980/extras/84e5015f23f44ae910f8501164417bd6.poster.avif?t=1771619706\" width=568 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133980/extras/84e5015f23f44ae910f8501164417bd6.webm?t=1771619706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133980/extras/84e5015f23f44ae910f8501164417bd6.mp4?t=1771619706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tYou can edit the maze or make creative designs with the maze editor.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\tYou can share your creation on the workshop.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
